//🔥💲 Method2:- 💲🔥

//💲 As for "pre-order-traversing":- ess method se according apnko sbse phle apnko har node pe left-side meh hypen-line-mark kr deni hai, and after that apnko from the "root"-node from left-side-of-tree se bas-always tree ki boundary(or mtlb tree-ki-walls) k along-along chalna hai and bich rashteh meh jo bhi hypen-line-mark cut hove toh usske node apnko apne "traversing-result" meh likh lena hai. 💲

//💲 and for "in-order-traversing":- apnko har node k bottom-side meh hypen-line-mark krni hai and then voh root-node se from the left-side-of-tree just-only-on-bas-boundary k along move krna hai and bich rashteh meh jo bhi node ki hypen-line cut hogi usko apnko apne "traversing-result" meh mark kr lena hai.. 💲

//💲 and for "post-order-traversing":- apnko har node k right-side meh hypen-line-mark krni hai then baad meh as same it is vohi kaam krna hai jo apn "pre-order" and "in-order" k liyeh krteh the... 💲
